Common.Strapline.Common.Text: POSITION, POSITION, POSITION – OPPOSITE DFS GALLERIA & LOUIS VUITTON

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE are proud to exclusively present this outstanding leasing opportunity in the heart of Mackay’s established Mount Pleasant large format retail precinct.  This prime 1,920sqm* showroom is the final tenancy currently available in newly refurbished ‘Amart Furniture Centre’, located at 7-15 Greenfield Blvd, Mount Pleasant.  

The tenancy ‘ticks all the boxes’ for large format retail with a functional / regular shape, high internal clearance, reverse cycle air conditioning, shopfront car parking, access to rear loading, excellent exposure and branding (STCA), and direct sight-lines from the highly trafficked Bruce Highway.  

Adjoining the tenancy is a 2,660sqm* concrete apron which could be used for a variety of purposes, such as a display yard for certain businesses, or to expand the tenancy to provide up to 4,580sqm* of GLA if required.

The centre benefits from excellent accessibility, being only 550m* by road from the Bruce Highway on and off ramps, and an abundance of on-grade car parking for some 294* vehicles (3.18* bays per 100sqm of GLA).   

The centre is located only 150m* from the Mount Pleasant Centre, a major sub-regional shopping centre with Woolworths, Coles, Kmart and over 70 specialty stores, and is surrounded by other major retailers, some of which highlighted below:

Amart Furniture, World Gym, BCC Cinemas, Petbarn, Amcal Pharmacy, Red Rooster, Autobarn, Intersport, Silly Solly's, Clark Rubber, Outdoor Living, Nightowl, Woolworths, Coles, Kmart.

For more information, please contact the exclusive CBRE leasing agents – Andrew Brimson and Sam Macgregor.

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: NOW LEASING – FINAL SHOWROOM IN MACKAY’S NEW ‘AMART FURNITURE CENTRE’

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE are pleased to exclusively present Warwick’s most exciting large format retail leasing opportunity – 20 Albion Street.  Supercheap Auto are relocating to a larger premises nearby and, as such, 20 Albion Street will be available for occupation from January 2021.

This prominent ‘standalone’ building has a GLAR of approx. 663sqm and features a high level of onsite car parking with approx. 21 bays (12 on-grade at the front and 9 undercroft at the rear) – a ratio of approx. 3.17 bays per 100sqm of GLAR.

The building is of modern tilt panel construction, providing high-quality, functional space suitable for a wide variety of uses (STCA).  The property also offers outstanding façade and pylon signage opportunities, along with the ability to brand the entire building façade (STCA). 

The site has excellent exposure to high volumes of vehicular traffic along Albion Street, which is part of the major road network where both the Cunningham (east-west) and the New England (north-south) Highways converge into a single carriageway and run concurrently for approx. 14km before separating again.

The site is well located in the heart of Warwick’s established retail and commercial precinct – the administrative centre for the entire Southern Downs Regional Council area, servicing an estimated resident population of 35,601 (2018) for the Region.  

For more information, please contact the exclusive CBRE leasing agents – Andrew Brimson and Sam Macgregor.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
THE OFFER
On offer is a brand new “state of the art” 62 single bedroom
accommodation facility developed as part of the existing a nursing home and residential aged care facility and is currently now surplus to the owner’s needs due to the main building still in ramp up.
The owners are prepared to offer a short- or long-term lease
arrangement and are prepared to discuss modifications to suit an individual requirement. 
The building adjoins the Infinite Care Aged Care Facility in Oregon St and has never been occupied. The building can be fully serviced from the existing residential aged care facility as has a fully operating kitchen and laundry.

The building is setup to support for NDIS, Transitional Care, Respite Care, Rehabilitation and many other uses.

+ Offices and meeting rooms

+ Fully air-conditioned
